frames.caption: A mysterious figure with horned features stands in a graveyard, holding an open book. The background is filled with tombstones and bare trees, creating an eerie atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set in a foggy graveyard, where a sinister-looking figure with horns is engrossed in a book. The setting is atmospheric and gothic, with tombstones and leafless trees enhancing the spooky vibe.

frames.caption: A mysterious figure with large, curved horns stands in the foreground, holding an open book. Two shadowy figures in dark robes stand behind, adding to the ominous atmosphere. The setting appears to be outdoors, with bare trees and a cross visible in the background.
frames.description: The scene depicts a dark, possibly ritualistic setting with a central figure resembling a demonic entity reading from a book. The presence of robed figures and a cross suggests a gothic or supernatural theme.
